title: 2 BRs Apt 4 rent - Putnam Properties - 2500 Pleasant - 9/1
posting_body: ['2 BEDROOMs - 2500 Pleasant Ave S - $1345-1395 - SEPT 1ST - PET FRIENDLY!!', 'The quaint, well- maintained building has 2 Bedrooms available for Sept 1st move in!!', 'Top floor and 2nd floor available!', 'Great neighborhood, large homes and quiet.', 'Close to Aldi, CC Club, Eat Street and More!', 'Building has well landscaped yard, great for tranquil setting and pets!', 'Units have Wood flooring in living room and kitchens, large space 950 sq feet!', 'Wood trimmed vintage peek-a-boo opening from eat-in kitchen to see into Living room!', 'Unit has huge living room and dining room space!', 'Updated kitchens with dishwasher.', 'Micro wave available upon request at no charge.', 'Large closets and linen and broom  closet in hall.', 'Tub and shower in vintage tiled bathroom.', 'Carpeted bedrooms.', 'You pay electric and internet.', 'Off street parking, heat ,water, trash included in rent.', ' Reserved garage parking available for $50 extra.', 'Updated laundry room and machines coin operated.', 'Caretaker on site.', 'Resident portal for all rent payments and maintenance requests.', '24 hour maintenance, great customer service.', 'Pets welcome!', 'Dogs up to 50 lbs.', 'or cats ok.', 'Limit two pets.', 'Pet rent $35 per month plus one time fee of $300 per pet.', 'Common area, well maintained!', 'Schedule a tour right away!', 'Call Nancy@', 'show contact info', 'Nancy @ putnamproperties .', 'net', 'Check out our  Google Reviews!!!', 'Or Visit us at:', '<URL>', '<URL>', 'Information in this ad, including price and amenities, subject to verification by Putnam Properties']
